Jampack

Class Rand

  • java.lang.Object
    • Jampack.Rand

  • public class Rand
extends Object
    The rand suite generates random objects with elements distributed randomly on [0,1] or normally with mean zero and standard deviation one.
    Version:
    Pre-alpha
    Author:
    G. W. Stewart
